- The refinement loop: prompt -> evaluate against rubric -> identify gaps -> refine -> repeat
- 2-3 concrete examples beat verbose prose for format consistency
- Test-driven iteration: share specific failures, not vague descriptions
- `/compact` manages context growth during multi-iteration sessions
- Stop when score plateaus across two iterations -- diminishing returns

