**Q3.** You want to run an agentic extraction loop (tool calls, validation, retry) on 5,000 documents. Can you use the Batches API?

**A.** Yes -- batch supports any API request format including multi-turn tool calling
**B.** No -- batch processes each request independently. Multi-turn agentic loops are not supported. Use synchronous API, or restructure as single-turn extraction with post-processing validation.
**C.** Yes, if you set tool_choice to any in the batch request
