- Message Batches API: 50% cost savings, up to 24-hour window, no latency SLA
- Decision rule: anyone waiting? --> real-time. Nobody waiting? --> batch
- custom_id correlates each result with its source request -- essential for failure handling
- Resubmit only failed items (by custom_id), not the entire batch
- Batch does NOT support multi-turn agentic loops (single request/response only)
- Refine prompts on 10-20 synchronous requests before submitting large batches

